PMET 2016 Results

Punjab Medical Entrance Test which is more frequently known as PMET. This entrance exam is organized by the Baba Farid University of Health Sciences. This entrance is held for providing admissions to the eligible candidates in different graduate level courses in Medicine and Dental Education. This entrance is for admission in the courses like MBBS, BDS, BAMS and BHMS. The university conducts the state level entrance exam for all the candidates wishing to study different Medical field. PMET enables the candidate to take admission in the Medical colleges in the Punjab University and other attached Medical Colleges in the state both private and government-aided colleges of Punjab.

Responsiblity

I hereby declare that the information present above is true to my knowledge. I will not be responsible for any inconsistency found. This project is only for educational purposes only.
